name: Wang_Farren
description:
This one's about communities created by deadilnes. Those teams that are brought together by that feeling of not-enough-time, "shipping" whatever you've got, alongside others' ships, maybe colliding with a few, but everyone's going the same way.

I tried to make this with only circles and circle-parts 'cause I think they're the most "communal" shape, but didn't quite manage it.
